SECTION 9: I(2) AND I(3) TOGETHER — INFORMATION CONTENT
======================================================================

If only α₁, α₂ nonzero (valid for n ≤ 8):
  α₂ = (2·I(3) - 3·H + 1) / 6
  α₁ = (H - 1 - 4·α₂) / 2

  H=  1, I3=   1: α₁=0 (formula:0.0), α₂=0 (formula:0.0) ✓
  H=  3, I3=   4: α₁=1 (formula:1.0), α₂=0 (formula:0.0) ✓
